    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《佛兰德斯的狗》是一款改编自英国作家奥维达同名小说的冒险类游戏。游戏的背景设定在19世纪末第一次工业革命时期的比利时。玩家将扮演安特卫普附近小村庄的一个穷苦少年尼洛，饥寒交迫却以画画作为自己的信仰和生存方式。在残酷的现实中，理想能否得以实现？玩家将与主角一起经历一段刻骨铭心的历程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以自己决定体验故事的顺序。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/be3a3c3568f65b9a5c05bcdfe12e7cec.poster.avif?t=1762691166\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/be3a3c3568f65b9a5c05bcdfe12e7cec.webm?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/be3a3c3568f65b9a5c05bcdfe12e7cec.mp4?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的选择会对故事走向产生不同的影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/ae95523fd68310af75ddac56bedbf69a.poster.avif?t=1762691166\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/ae95523fd68310af75ddac56bedbf69a.webm?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/ae95523fd68310af75ddac56bedbf69a.mp4?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏世界各处自由创作属于自己的绘画作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/34cffb5545b590d99001b40774f46d09.poster.avif?t=1762691166\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/34cffb5545b590d99001b40774f46d09.webm?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/34cffb5545b590d99001b40774f46d09.mp4?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受比利时佛兰德斯地区的美丽风景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/5dd1267e38dc33c4d445024008c72ba4.poster.avif?t=1762691166\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/5dd1267e38dc33c4d445024008c72ba4.webm?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/5dd1267e38dc33c4d445024008c72ba4.mp4?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受19世纪比利时佛兰德斯地区特有的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/64789bf0635946161c12cbe7b5502f95.poster.avif?t=1762691166\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/64789bf0635946161c12cbe7b5502f95.webm?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1806290/extras/64789bf0635946161c12cbe7b5502f95.mp4?t=1762691166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和狗狗帕奇进行有趣的交互。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai